{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-product","blocks":{"text_1":{"type":"text","settings":{"column":"left","text":"<p>Organic. All-Natural. Parrot Safe Materials.</p>","text_style":"body","text_block_size":"small","show_text_background":true,"margin_top":0,"color_scheme_1":"option-4","hide_quick_view":true}},"title":{"type":"title","settings":{"column":"left","heading_size":"large","margin_top":0,"hide_quick_view":false}},"product-meta":{"type":"product-meta","settings":{"column":"left","show_product_inventory":true,"text_style":"uppercase","inventory_threshold":51,"show_inventory_quantity":false,"show_product_sku":false,"margin_top":0,"hide_quick_view":true}},"price":{"type":"price","settings":{"column":"left","price_size":"small","badge_discount":false,"margin_top":0,"hide_quick_view":false}},"spacer_1":{"type":"spacer","settings":{"column":"left","margin_top":0,"hide_quick_view":false}},"delivery_estimator":{"type":"delivery_estimator","settings":{"column":"left","delivery_estimator_text":"Est. Delivery between","earliest_delivery":"1","latest_delivery":"4","color_scheme_1":"option-2","margin_top":10,"hide_mobile":false,"hide_desktop":false,"hide_quick_view":true}},"description":{"type":"description","settings":{"column":"left","margin_top":0,"text_size":"medium","hide_quick_view":false}},"collapsible_tab_cn6ffN":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"column":"left","heading":"Features and Benefits","heading_size":"medium","heading_tag":"h4","icon":"check_mark","no_padding":true,"content":"<p>{{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.features_and_benefits | metafield_tag }}</p><p></p>","page":"","custom_liquid":"{{ product.metafields.custom.features_and_benefits | newline_to_br }}","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"show_spacer":false,"margin_top":10,"color_scheme_1":"option-1","hide_quick_view":true}},"collapsible_tab_tGJEdy":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"column":"left","heading":"How to Use","heading_size":"medium","heading_tag":"h4","icon":"question_mark","no_padding":true,"content":"<p>{{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.how_to_use | metafield_tag }}</p><p></p>","page":"","custom_liquid":"{{ product.metafields.custom.how_to_use | newline_to_br }}","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"show_spacer":false,"margin_top":10,"color_scheme_1":"option-1","hide_quick_view":true}},"collapsible_tab_nFwUBQ":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"column":"left","heading":"Why Your Bird Will Love It","heading_size":"medium","heading_tag":"h4","icon":"bag_heart","no_padding":true,"content":"<p>{{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.why_your_bird_will_love_it | metafield_tag }}</p><p></p>","page":"","custom_liquid":"{{ product.metafields.custom.why_your_bird_will_love_it | newline_to_br }}","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"show_spacer":false,"margin_top":5,"color_scheme_1":"option-1","hide_quick_view":true}},"collapsible_tab_ifGyQ8":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"column":"left","heading":"Shipping & Returns","heading_size":"medium","heading_tag":"h4","icon":"truck","no_padding":true,"content":"<p>If you’re looking to return or exchange your order for whatever reason, we're here to help! We offer <strong>free returns</strong> within <strong>30 days </strong>of purchase. You can return your product for<strong> store credit</strong>, <strong>a different product</strong>, or a <strong>refund </strong>to the original payment method.</p>","page":"","custom_liquid":"","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"show_spacer":false,"margin_top":10,"color_scheme_1":"option-1","hide_quick_view":true}},"spacer_2":{"type":"spacer","settings":{"column":"left","margin_top":0,"hide_quick_view":true}},"collapsible_tab_2":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"column":"left","heading":"Support","heading_size":"medium","heading_tag":"h4","icon":"headset","no_padding":true,"content":"<p>Questions about sizing, safety, or your order? Email us at support@squawkshop.com or use our contact form. We'll help you choose the right products for your bird and reply as soon as possible during business hours.</p>","page":"","custom_liquid":"","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"show_spacer":false,"margin_top":0,"color_scheme_1":"option-1","hide_quick_view":true}},"spacer_3":{"type":"spacer","settings":{"column":"left","margin_top":0,"hide_quick_view":true}},"tabs":{"type":"tabs","settings":{"column":"left","heading_1":"Returns & Exchanges","row_content_1":"<p><em><strong>Easy returns and hassle-free exchanges.</strong></em> If you're not completely satisfied, you can return or exchange your items within 30 days. For hygiene and safety, items must be unused unless there is a defect or issue with your order. We want you and your bird to be truly happy with every purchase.</p>","heading_2":"Delivery Info","row_content_2":"<p><em><strong>Getting your parrots goodies to you, fast.</strong></em><br/>We partner with trusted carriers to make sure your orders reach you quickly and safely, no matter where you are.</p>","heading_3":"Help & Support","row_content_3":"<p><em><strong>Always here to assist you.</strong></em><br/>Questions about our products or your order? Our friendly support team is ready to help anytime you need.</p>","centered_tabs":false,"remove_border_tabs":false,"margin_top":0,"hide_quick_view":false}},"buy_buttons":{"type":"buy_buttons","settings":{"column":"left","show_dynamic_checkout":true,"force_unbranded_button":false,"show_gift_card_recipient":true,"stack_buttons_desktop":false,"stacked_buttons_width":"default","picker_type":"button","swatch_shape":"circle","margin_top":10,"margin_bottom":0,"hide_unavailable":false,"hide_quantity_input":false,"hide_mobile":false,"hide_desktop":false,"hide_quick_view":false}},"complementary":{"type":"complementary","settings":{"column":"left","block_heading":"Goes well with","product_list_limit":10,"image_ratio":"square","enable_quick_add":false,"columns":"two","disable_arrow_mobile":true,"color_scheme_1":"","margin_top":10,"hide_quick_view":true}},"collapsible_tab_4":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"column":"under-gallery","heading":"Gizmo the Grey Bird's Story & Mission","heading_size":"large","heading_tag":"h4","icon":"none","no_padding":true,"image":"shopify://shop_images/Meet_The_Flock_Behind_the_Squawk_2400_x_2400_px_1.png","content":"<p>After spending over 16 years trapped in a cage with no enrichment, no toys, and no real life, Gizmo’s journey became our inspiration. His resilience reminds us how deeply parrots rely on proper stimulation, love, and freedom to thrive. That’s why Squawk Shop is dedicated to giving birds around the world access to safe, premium, and affordable enrichment—so no parrot ever has to go without the joy and quality of life they deserve.</p>","page":"","custom_liquid":"","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"show_spacer":false,"margin_top":10,"color_scheme_1":"option-1","hide_quick_view":true}},"collapsible_tab_5":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"column":"under-gallery","heading":"Product Ingredients","heading_size":"large","heading_tag":"h4","icon":"none","no_padding":true,"content":"","page":"","custom_liquid":"","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"show_spacer":false,"margin_top":10,"color_scheme_1":"option-1","hide_quick_view":true}},"text_2":{"type":"text","settings":{"column":"under-gallery","text":"<h3>⭐ Limited time offer ⭐ - Up to 20% Sale</h3><p>\"Hurry! Save up to 20% on this item for a limited time only!\" Grab the deal before it's gone!</p>","text_style":"body","text_block_size":"small","show_text_background":true,"margin_top":25,"color_scheme_1":"option-4","hide_quick_view":true}},"purchase_trust":{"type":"text","settings":{"column":"left","text":"<p>Fast shipping &bull; 30-day returns &bull; Secure checkout</p>","text_style":"body","text_block_size":"small","show_text_background":true,"margin_top":5,"color_scheme_1":"option-2","hide_quick_view":true}}},"block_order":["text_1","title","product-meta","price","delivery_estimator","description","buy_buttons","purchase_trust","complementary","spacer_1","collapsible_tab_cn6ffN","collapsible_tab_tGJEdy","collapsible_tab_nFwUBQ","collapsible_tab_ifGyQ8","spacer_2","collapsible_tab_2","spacer_3","tabs","collapsible_tab_4","collapsible_tab_5","text_2"],"settings":{"enable_full_width":false,"enable_sticky_info":true,"sticky_content":"content","product_gallery_width":45,"gallery_layout":"thumbnail_slider","media_position":"left","media_fit":"cover","thumbnail_size":"large","image_zoom":"lightbox","hide_variants":false,"enable_video_looping":false,"quantity_selector":4,"color_scheme":"option-1","in_stock_background_color":"#fffd96","in_stock_color":"#2f3d45","under_gallery":"second","mobile_thumbnails":"hide","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36,"ignore_spacing":false}},"1763676936a0e47fba":{"type":"apps","settings":{"include_margins":true,"padding_top":12,"padding_bottom":12}},"collapsible_content_HhLeH7":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"collapsible_row_phzN8Q":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"What is cuttlebone for birds?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>Cuttlebone is the internal shell of a cuttlefish. Birds use it as a natural calcium source and to help maintain beak condition.</p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_FxbfCY":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"How often should I offer cuttlebone?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>Most birds can have access regularly, but it should complement (not replace) a balanced diet. If your bird over-consumes, limit access and check with an avian vet.</p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_gQ6GLX":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Is cuttlebone safe for parrots?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>Generally yes, when it’s bird-safe and replaced if it becomes dirty, moldy, or breaks into sharp pieces.</p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_BkVAJz":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"What size cuttlebone should I buy?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>Small birds often prefer smaller pieces; medium to large birds usually do better with larger sizes like 8” so they can grip and use it comfortably.</p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_Rj3mXU":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Cuttlebone vs “squid bone” is there a difference?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>People say “squid bone,” but most products sold are cuttlebone (cuttlefish). Either way, it’s used for calcium + beak support.</p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["collapsible_row_phzN8Q","collapsible_row_FxbfCY","collapsible_row_gQ6GLX","collapsible_row_BkVAJz","collapsible_row_Rj3mXU"],"name":"t:sections.collapsible_content.presets.name","settings":{"caption":"","text_style":"caption-with-letter-spacing","text_size":"medium","heading":"Cuttlebone for Birds: FAQ","heading_size":"medium","heading_style":"default","heading_tag":"h2","heading_alignment":"center","open_first_collapsible_row":true,"open_all_collapsible_row":false,"color_scheme":"","color_scheme_1":"","padding_top":96,"padding_bottom":96,"ignore_spacing":false,"margin_spacing":"negative","margin_top":0}},"testimonials":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"column_1":{"type":"column","settings":{"rating":true,"rating_stars":"5-star","text":"<p>My Blue and Gold Macaw absolutely love how big these toys are from Squawk Shop. I like to hide nuts in the rattan balls for him to go foraging.</p>","title":"— Kelsey C. · Verified Buyer","image":"shopify://shop_images/Screenshot_2025-11-20_at_3.19.25_PM.png","hide_image":false,"product":"ball-thing-monster"}},"column_2":{"type":"column","settings":{"rating":true,"rating_stars":"5-star","text":"<p>I’ve never seen my African Grey this happy! The Java Tree we ordered was exactly the one shown online, and the quality is unbelievable. The natural branches encourage climbing, chewing, and exploring every day. It’s stunning in our living room and has completely transformed his daily routine. Squawk Shop genuinely cares about birds, and you can feel it in every product.</p>","title":"— Brenda R. · Verified Buyer","image":"shopify://shop_images/20251120_1525_Woman_with_Parrot_simple_compose_01kahnxkw6epmsz1dx66fydw6n.png","hide_image":false,"product":"java-tree-4"}},"column_3":{"type":"column","settings":{"rating":true,"rating_stars":"5-star","text":"<p>We purchased a new cage and were blown away by the quality. The free essentials bundle was such a thoughtful addition and made setup incredibly easy. Everything was packaged perfectly and arrived in pristine condition. My conure has so much more space now, and I feel confident knowing everything is bird-safe and built to last.</p>","title":"— Alisha T. · Verified Buyer","image":"shopify://shop_images/close-up-of-parakeet-biting-finger-534563317-5b554aecc9e77c003712b1f9.jpg","hide_image":false,"product":"majestic-series-medium-cage-bundle"}},"column_4":{"type":"column","settings":{"rating":true,"rating_stars":"5-star","text":"<p>This cat toilet is a game-changer! It’s spacious, easy to clean, and fits perfectly in my home. My cat feels comfortable and happy using it every day. The design is sleek and modern, blending seamlessly with my decor.</p>","title":"James Martin","hide_image":false,"product":""}},"column_5":{"type":"column","settings":{"rating":true,"rating_stars":"5-star","text":"<p>Since switching to Mellow Dream, my cat’s calmness has noticeably improved. She’s more relaxed and sleeps better through the night. The natural ingredients really make a difference—highly recommend for any cat with anxiety!</p>","title":"Sophia Johnson","hide_image":false,"product":""}},"column_6":{"type":"column","settings":{"rating":true,"rating_stars":"5-star","text":"<p>The waterproof raincoat keeps my dog dry and comfortable during rainy walks. It fits perfectly and doesn’t restrict movement. Plus, it’s easy to put on and take off — highly recommend!</p>","title":"Liam Wilson","hide_image":false,"product":""}}},"block_order":["column_1","column_2","column_3","column_4","column_5","column_6"],"settings"